imdb.plot outline: An Orpheus and Eurydice tale of the 20th century - a dramatic story of a country girl, Tatyana, and her difficult fate, told against the background of the most difficult Soviet period - of collectivization, repression, war - and the eternal story of love, parting, a long, arduous journey and the long-awaited reunion of lovers.
